      "markText": "他只知道持续了几个月的和平像一件穿得太久的衣服，已经变得松松垮垮。",
      "totalCount": 540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017346&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=529&rangeEnd=808",
