    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017346_26_6205-6224",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "6205-6224",
      "markText": "这就是我们跟随泽农能走到的最远的地方。",
      "totalCount": 480,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017346&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=6205&rangeEnd=6224",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fee321f0813ab6d46g016166?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=6205&rangeEnd=6224"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017346_3_789-877",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "789-877",
      "markText": "我将你置于世界的中央，以便让你更好地静观世间万物。我塑造的你既不属于天界，也不属于凡间，既非必死，也非永生，以便让你自己像一个好画家或者灵巧的雕塑家那样，自由地完成自己的形体。",
      "totalCount": 476,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017346&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=789&rangeEnd=877",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fee321f0813ab6d46g016166?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=789&rangeEnd=877"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017346_4_3912-3935",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3912-3935",
      "markText": "我的双脚在世界上游荡，就像昆虫在圣诗集上爬行。",
